{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My brother Tsvi went to my brother Altar and my-- and I went to brother Darvas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Darvas, his wife was very sick at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had five children, two sons, three daughters, all college, college graduates.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they didn't speak Yiddish because they spoke Hungarian in the house and Romanian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I didn't know Romanian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I came into the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The only one I could speak was with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My aunt knew a little bit German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She understood Yiddish a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But she wasn't too long in that house because she, she was sent to the city of Debrecen because she was very sick, and she died a half a year later.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Here are we are in, in Satu Mare again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And in Satu Mare, I stayed-- this was-- this was the end of October.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I stayed November, December, and January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Three months I stayed with my Uncle Darvas hiding out in that-- in that-- in his house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was a retired teacher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He used to go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "His wife [INAUDIBLE] who was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She died later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The younger daughter was in college.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The, the older daughter was married and away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there was another one that was home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And, and the only way I was able to communicate was I had to-- I had to talk in Hungarian, which I picked up very fast.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "If you don't-- if you have no choice, you learn it fast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I suffered terribly from hunger in that house because they were retired teachers, and they were living on a pension.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And in the city at that time the, the people were getting rations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Bread was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Fat was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Milk was rationed, everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
